<span style="font-weight: 400;">According to her, the main cause of colon cancer is: </span><b>Secret grief or deep hurt. Long standing resentments.¬†</b>

<span style="font-weight: 400;">One of the ways of healing this is through saying or writing affirmations.¬†</span>

